<div id="pf5a" class="pf w3 hf" data-page-no="5a"><div class="pc pc5a w3 hf"><div class="t m2a7 x11 h25 yea ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 11 </div><div class="t m16 x6f h25 y53e ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m349 x50 h25 y252 ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 10-16 </div><div class="t m68a x8a h19 yb92 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Do a Bible </div><div class="t m6a9 xaf h19 y30 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word Study </div><div class="t m6aa x64 h19 y406 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;\\N </div><div class="t m2f2 x11 h1f yb76 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath Afternoon </div><div class="t m5c6 x11 h20 yb93 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Lev. 19:11-16; Psalm 12; </div><div class="t m59b x5 h20 yace ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prov. 30:5, 6; Matt. 5:13-16; 20:26; Luke 10:29-42; Rom. 6:15-</div><div class="t m211 x5 h20 y5c8 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23. </div><div class="t m473 x2e h20 yb94 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;And the King will answer and say to </div><div class="t m3f8 x2e h20 yb95 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them, &apos;Assuredly, I say to you, inasmuch as you did it to one of </div><div class="t m6ab x2e h20 yafc ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the least of these My brethren, you did it to Me&apos; &quot; (Matthew </div><div class="t m605 x2e h20 yb96 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25:40, NKJV). </div><div class="t me7 x4 h20 yafd ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHT: </div><div class="t m541 xc5 h21 yafd ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This lesson seeks to demonstrate the effec-</div><div class="t m440 x5 h21 y26b ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tiveness of Bible word studies. The word we will study is </div><div class="t m147 x5b h21 y5cb ff5 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">service. </div><div class="t me8 x5 h21 yb97 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One way the gospel becomes real to others is by acts of kindness, </div><div class="t m6ac x5 h21 y5b8 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compassion, and unselfishness performed by those who value the gift </div><div class="t m15d x5 h21 yb98 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of salvation and fulfill their responsibility to the world. </div><div class="t m279 x4 h20 y5cf ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WHAT IS SERVICE ALL ABOUT? </div><div class="t m1d9 x9d h21 yb99 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service can take many </div><div class="t m2ee x5 h21 y5d0 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forms. It may be practical service to those in need, service of various </div><div class="t mc4 x5 h21 y5d1 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kinds for the church, witnessing to the centrality of Jesus in our lives, </div><div class="t m42d x11 h21 y5d2 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">or teaching others God&apos;s special message for the last days. Whatever </div><div class="t m6ad x5 h21 y5d3 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is, we place ourselves at God&apos;s disposal to be His instruments. </div><div class="t m12c x5 h21 y5d4 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service is part of our sanctification; we are set apart to be used by </div><div class="t m2ce x11 h21 y5d5 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. Service can bring peace to families, communities, churches, </div><div class="t m6ae x5 h21 y10c ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to our own lives through presenting Jesus as the answer to human </div><div class="t m658 x5 h21 y5d7 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need. Service implements mercy and justice in our relationships with </div><div class="t m68d x11 h21 yb9a ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others. </div><div class="t m106 x5 h21 y53d ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">88 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
